If you think the military weapons of today are mind-blowing wait until you see the weapons of the future. Ex-Navy SEAL Richard "Mack" Machowicz travels the globe to find some of the most lethal and sinister armaments yet devised. With Mack firing everything from smart missiles to futuristic lasers never-before-attempted test firings will leave you shocked and amazed.
